java.util.List<SObject> frame = new java.util.ArrayList<>(); for (int k = 0; k < objArr.length(); k++) frame.add(new SObject(objArr.getJSONObject(k))); cachedSfnFrames.add(frame);
} } catch (Exception e) { cachedSfnFrames = null; } }
	public void setRoot(int newRoot) { if (newRoot == rootIdx || newRoot < 0 || newRoot >= pts.length / 2) return; int curr = newRoot; int prev = -1; while (curr != -1) { int nxt = parents[curr]; parents[curr] = prev; prev = curr; curr = nxt; if (prev == rootIdx) break; } rootIdx = newRoot; calculateLengths(); }
	public void initParents() { parents = new int[pts.length / 2]; for (int i = 0; i < parents.length; i++) parents[i] = -1;
		if (type == 0 || type == 13) { parents[0] = 1; parents[1] = 2; parents[3] = 1; parents[4] = 3; parents[5] = 1; parents[6] = 5; parents[7] = 2; parents[8] = 7; parents[9] = 2; parents[10] = 9; } else if (type == 2) { for (int i = 1; i < parents.length; i++) parents[i] = i - 1; } else if (type == 3) { parents[1] = 0; parents[2] = 0; } else if (type == 4) { parents[0] = 1; parents[1] = -1; } else if (type == 1) { parents[1] = 0; } else if (type == 5 || type == 6) { for (int i = 1; i < parents.length; i++) parents[i] = 0; } else if (type >= 10 && type <= 16) { parents[0] = -1; } else if (type >= 7 && type <= 9) { if (parents.length > 1) parents[1] = 0; } else { for (int i = 0; i < parents.length; i++) if (i != rootIdx) parents[i] = rootIdx; } }
	public void calculateLengths() { if (pts == null) return; lens = new float[pts.length / 2]; for (int i = 0; i < pts.length / 2; i++) { if (i == rootIdx) continue; int p = parents[i]; if (p != -1) lens[i] = dist(i, p); } }
	private float dist(int i1, int i2) { return (float) Math.hypot(pts[i1 * 2] - pts[i2 * 2], pts[i1 * 2 + 1] - pts[i2 * 2 + 1]); }
	public void ensureArrays() { int req = pts.length / 2; if (jointTypes == null || jointTypes.length != req) { int[] t = new int[req]; for (int i = 0; i < Math.min(req, (jointTypes == null ? 0 : jointTypes.length)); i++) t[i] = jointTypes[i]; jointTypes = t; } 
	if (formTypes == null || formTypes.length != req) { int[] t = new int[req]; for (int i = 0; i < Math.min(req, (formTypes == null ? 0 : formTypes.length)); i++) t[i] = formTypes[i]; formTypes = t; } 
	if (dotTypes == null || dotTypes.length != req) { int[] t = new int[req]; for (int i = 0; i < Math.min(req, (dotTypes == null ? 0 : dotTypes.length)); i++) t[i] = dotTypes[i]; dotTypes = t; } 
	if (linkedIds == null || linkedIds.length != req) { String[] t = new String[req]; for (int i=0; i<req; i++) t[i] = (linkedIds!=null && i<linkedIds.length) ? linkedIds[i] : ""; linkedIds = t; } 
